
A modular ROS2-based robotics platform for autonomous service and event robots, combining sensor fusion, perception, navigation, 
human-robot interaction and AI modules such as object detection, speech interaction and face recognition.

The project demonstrates a system-level architecture for intelligent robots using Edge/Cloud integration, simulation, 
digital twins and AI-based decision support.

